  "content": "        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;\">E2E Test + PR + Merge</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Integration tests, happy path, edge cases, then open and merge PR</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"insight-box\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n    <p>The skill file orchestrates other skills: brainstorming, plan writing, subagent-driven development. When Layer 1 is solid, the brainstorm phase becomes a quick validation, not a creative session.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">07 / 09</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 8: THE RESULTS -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">The Results</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    13 Issues.<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-green\">13 PRs Merged.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    The tiered knowledge feature went from RFC to fully shipped through this two-layer system.\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Stats -->\n  <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    <div class=\"stat-box\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-blue);\">1</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px;\">RFC written</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"stat-box\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-amber);\">13</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px;\">Issues generated</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"stat-box\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-green);\">13</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px;\